review_blob: One of the hidden secrets. Very drinkable beer from the brewery with great brewing tradition.
Well, what can I say. It is different.
I am quite surprised that some people consider it bad beer. I drank much worse.
Best of Slovakian beers. Very pleasent taste.
One of the great beers in the world. While visiting Prague, do not forget to drink one of the tap.
Drinkable, but not what I would call a quality beer.
